---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page>
  <section class="py-16 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Unlock Revenue Growth with Smarter Systems</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Tailored CRM automation, ad strategy, and lead management designed to turn more conversations into customers.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Starter Systems Package</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
        Your CRM and sales workflow audit + action plan to stop lead leakage and create efficient automations.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li>Deep-dive CRM workflow audit</li>
        <li>1-hour strategy consultation</li>
        <li>CRM automations setup for lead nurturing (up to 3 automations)</li>
        <li>Basic integrations with key tools (Calendly, Sheets, Zapier)</li>
        <li>Lead tracking framework creation (Google Sheet / CRM dashboard)</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <a href="https://calendly.com/reachout2brady" target="_blank" 
           class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg shadow transition">
          Schedule a Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Build Beyond the Basics</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li><strong>✏️ Additional Automations Setup:</strong> Automate new steps beyond your starter package</li>
        <li><strong>🔗 Advanced Integrations:</strong> CRM → Google Sheets, Email marketing, SMS, Ads, Dispatch systems</li>
        <li><strong>📈 Performance Ads Setup & Management:</strong> Meta Ads or TikTok Ads launch + optimization</li>
        <li><strong>🛠️ CRM Clean-up and Rebuild:</strong> Fixing messy fields, old lists, broken workflows</li>
        <li><strong>📊 Monthly Support & Optimization:</strong> Ongoing monthly check-ins to improve</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Your Solo Growth Partner</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li>Built for small businesses (no big agency red tape)</li>
        <li>Practical, revenue-focused solutions — not tech for tech’s sake</li>
        <li>Personal commitment: You work directly with me, not an outsourced team</li>
        <li>Systems built for scale, not just quick fixes</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Ready to Stop Losing Leads?</h2>
    <a href="https://calendly.com/reachout2brady" target="_blank" 
       class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg shadow transition">
      Let’s Talk About Your Systems
    </a>
  </section>
</Page>
